### 문제 풀이 

```python 
import collections

class Solution:
    def findAnagrams(self, s: str, p: str) -> List[int]:
        answer = list()
        
        dict_p = collections.Counter(p)
        for i in range(len(s)-len(p)+1):
            dict_s = collections.Counter(s[i:i+len(p)])
            if dict_p == dict_s:
                answer.append(i)
        return answer
```
